## Integration flow

```
Phase 3 writes content-data.json
Phase 3.5 Quality Gate runs this rule
  → Identify violations
  → Auto-fix safe ones
  → Surface unsafe ones to user
  → User accepts fixes via Composer
  → Re-validate
  → PASS → Phase 4
```
